  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisite: Order of the Ghostslayer</em></p><p>As a bonus action, you curse a creature that you can see within 30 feet of you. Until the end of your next turn, any objects they are holding fall through their grasp including weapons and shields landing in an unoccupied space of your choice within 5 feet of the creature, and they are unable to interact with objects.<br /><br /><strong>Amplified</strong>. This curse lasts up to 1 minute. Starting after the end of your next turn, the cursed creature can make a Charisma saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the curse on itself on a success.</p>",
